text: Yehya Mohamed Hassanein (born 24 September 1944) is an Egyptian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 63 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Egypt Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Cairo
